            "The council sought to prelatise secular authority through ceremonial acts.",
            "Some writers use the term to describe attempts to prelatise administrative roles."
          ],
          "collocations": ["prelatise authority", "prelatise ceremonial"],
          "synonyms": [],
          "antonyms": [],
          "register": "formal",
          "domain": ["general"]
        }
      ]
